{
  "stem": "27509.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And out of these shreds they used to make new material.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and-- and what we used to produce there was blankets, army-- army uniforms or-- or-- or-- or army coats, the heavy army coats, and other forms of-- of-- of material.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With time, of course, it has improved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But even so, it had-- it had-- it had a full integrated industry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a integrated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There-- there were spinning mills.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were dye houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were-- there were looms and-- that-- that used to-- to-- to-- to do the actual.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the people who ran the looms were many of them-- many of them were outdoor people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had the loom put away in one of the rooms and take out some work so that the big manufacturer didn't have to-- to-- to keep big factories.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Some-- some did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But-- but there was a great deal of other work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When there was work, there was work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If not, you had to wait until the work came.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "How they managed in meantime, God only knows.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So that was the nature of Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, of course, being so-- so-- so self-assertive terms economic, they also-- and they had also their banks, their own co-operative banks to help the people in the trade to bridge both the shortage of cash because the entire economy was on promissory notes.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You used to run a business on promissory notes of 18 months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the early days of Israel, of Palestine, the situation was exactly the same.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the people who came from Russia and from Poland and from Romania to Israel didn't know anything else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "There was no ready cash, so the entire economy was based on long-term promissory notes.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
